{"tid":2176822,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警改口認非即場拘捕被告","createTime":"2020-08-27T10:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T10:37:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"097601014cf16319b109b3501ba613c2fc93d751","tid":2176822,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:12:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/L57Q47HLYZELHB2UZDZPF4553I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FL57Q47HLYZELHB2UZDZPF4553I%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=d32087f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FL57Q47HLYZELHB2UZDZPF4553I%2F&h=ceccf3fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/L57Q47HLYZELHB2UZDZPF4553I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警改口認非即場拘捕被告<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QV7wvEia84Xtxc6QeZjh2ysbE0w=/5184x3456/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WHRSLNGQJBHNHB3JR46YYPLQSI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQV7wvEia84Xtxc6QeZjh2ysbE0w%3D%2F5184x3456%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWHRSLNGQJBHNHB3JR46YYPLQSI.jpg&h=362c3505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年11月11日，多區有市民上街響應「三罷」行動。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【三罷堵路案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】兩名女學生涉去年11月三罷首天用交通雪糕筒及垃圾桶等堵塞港鐵港大站外道路，遭警員拘捕。二人否認在公眾地方造成阻礙罪昨受審。拘捕其中一名被告的警員供稱，接手處理被告後不久宣佈拘捕她，惟他在辯方盤問下改口，承認當時沒即場拘捕亦無警誡被告。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。道追捕以雜物阻塞行車線的黑衣人，至港大黃克競樓的樓梯後，接手處理被同袍截停的次被告，並在港大站A出口外以涉嫌在公眾地方行為不檢拘捕她。<br />\n<br />\n梁在盤問下稱，同袍警車到場不久，他乘坐的警車也到達。辯方播片，顯示數名黑衣人以雜物堵路後逃往港大校園，未幾只有。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同案兩人守行為<br />\n<br />\n盤問下梁承認沒在A出口外宣。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n拘捕第三被告的女警郭綺瑾接受辯方盤問時，起初否認到場時已不見黑衣人堵路，惟看片後承認確看不見黑衣人堵路，但見他們逃跑。郭承認沒在場警誡第三被告。<br />\n<br />\n另外兩被告早前准以簽保守行為方式結案。聆訊今續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC683/20"},{"pid":"602a0203dfd2cf04b934429d4ae0fd14cf385a61","tid":2176822,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"呢單係邊個裁判官審"},{"pid":"1b5695e53888fe246991f88811e36d71359e5dfa","tid":2176822,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:33:23.000Z","msg":"假口供無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbf8bb5d19b8301768d6afba5fdc9d4d8d80595","tid":2176822,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"咁又唔係妨礙司法公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690375fc66979b5f80d5a767c42544fff32f1c54","tid":2176822,"uid":120807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}